kneeleft.label: Knee Ranges of Motion Table A-3 page 598: AMA Estimated Normal: Flexion (150D), Extension (0D). Motion is measured with goniometer and is reported right over left side in Degrees (D).
kneeleft.textareatext: Hyper-extension is measured with a '+' preceeding the measurement. i.e. +10 = 10 degrees of hyper-extension.

kneeleft.label: Actual goniometer measurements of the range of motion are only required for PR-4 (Permanent & Stationary) reports. Visual estimates of the range of motion may be adequate for Doctor's First reports and PR-2 reports.
